Provides: cosmic-flux
Description: Live wallpaper daemon and applet for COSMIC desktop
 Flux renders GIF and video files as live wallpapers on the
 COSMIC desktop. It includes a Wayland layer-shell daemon (cosmic-ext-flux-daemon)
 and a COSMIC panel applet (cosmic-ext-applet-flux) for controlling playback,
 fit mode, FPS cap, and multi-monitor span mode.
